cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper is focused on developing a benchmark for evaluating meta-reinforcement learning and multi-task learning algorithms for robotic manipulation tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves computer vision techniques for perception, which makes cs.CV (Computer Vision) a likely category. Finally, the paper deals with control and optimization of robotic systems, which makes cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category as well.
